OL,3,CBodycam footage shows 'brave and bold'
OL,4,Cpolice officer arresting man with knife
OL,6,FThe officer's body-worn camera
OL,7,Fcaptures the moments leading up to the
OL,8,Farrest as well as him arresting the
OL,9,Fsuspect. (Pictures from Greater
OL,10,FManchester Police)
OL,12,FA "brave and bold" police officer has
OL,13,Fbeen commended for arresting a man
OL,14,Fcarrying a knife who threatened to
OL,15,Fharm him.
OL,17,FResponse Officer Anthony Spence made
OL,18,Fthe arrest in Hollins area of
OL,19,FRochdale, after being called out to
OL,20,Freports of an armed robbery.
