OL,6,FAs the first officer on the scene, PC
OL,7,FSpence carried out a search of the
OL,8,Farea moments after the suspect had
OL,9,Fgone into a local shop demanding
OL,10,Fcigarettes.
OL,12,FIt wasn't long before PC Spence found
OL,13,Fthe suspect on a nearby street, thanks
OL,14,Fto his distinctive clothing; a pink
OL,15,Fhoodie with large ears on the hood, as
OL,16,Fwell as pink trousers and a black
OL,17,Fjumper.
