OL,6,FThe officer approached the suspect,
OL,7,Fwho was waving around a large kitchen
OL,8,Fknife, and asked him to drop the
OL,9,Fweapon.
OL,11,FInstead, the suspect approached PC
OL,12,FSpence and made threatening comments.
OL,14,FIn footage from the officer's body-
OL,15,Fworn camera, the suspect can be heard
OL,16,Fsaying: "Get back in your car and
OL,17,Fdrive away."
