OL,6,FDespite the officer repeatedly asking
OL,7,Fthe suspect to get on the ground, he
OL,8,Fcontinued to approach and wave his
OL,9,Fweapon around.
OL,11,FAt this point, Officer Spence called
OL,12,Ffor back-up and informed the suspect
OL,13,Fhe had a taser. When this did not stop
OL,14,Fthe suspect from approaching, he fired
OL,15,Fthe taser.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/8
