OL,3,CBodycam footage shows 'brave and bold'
OL,4,Cpolice officer arresting man with knife
OL,6,FWhile the taser did not stop the
OL,7,Fsuspect, he stopped threatening the
OL,8,Fofficer and walked away. PC Spence
OL,9,Ffollowed the suspect to a nearby
OL,10,Fstreet, where he became a greater
OL,11,Fthreat to the community by knocking on
OL,12,Fthe doors of innocent members of the
OL,13,Fpublic.
OL,15,FSeizing on a moment of opportunity,
OL,16,FOfficer Spence managed to use his
OL,17,Fbaton to disarm the man and ensured he
OL,18,Fcould make a prompt arrest before any
OL,19,Fserious injury occurred.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/8
