OL,3,CBodycam footage shows 'brave and bold'
OL,4,Cpolice officer arresting man with knife
OL,6,FAs he is arrested, the suspect can be
OL,7,Fheard shouting: "I've been framed!"
OL,9,FThe 26-year-old man is currently still
OL,10,Fsectioned in hospital under the Mental
OL,11,FHealth Act on suspicion of robbery,
OL,12,Fthreats to kill and possession of a
OL,13,Fbladed article.
OL,15,FAs a result of his actions to serve
OL,16,Fand protect, PC Antony Spence was
OL,17,Fawarded for his brave efforts at a
OL,18,FChief Constable's Commendation event.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/8
