OL,4,Cpolice officer arresting man with knife
OL,6,FOn the incident and subsequent
OL,7,Frecognition, his Inspector said; "PC
OL,8,FAnthony Spence embodies what we want
OL,9,Four officers to be; brave and bold,
OL,10,Fupholding the values we agreed when we
OL,11,Ftake on the job.
OL,13,F"On that morning there was a real
OL,14,Fserious risk to life, not only his but
OL,15,Fmembers of the public, due to the
OL,16,Funpredictable nature of the person
OL,17,Fholding the knife.
