OL,6,F"In this one incident, we've managed
OL,7,Fto make Oldham a safer place and means
OL,8,Fwe can conduct an effective
OL,9,Finvestigation to ensure one less knife
OL,10,Fis off the street.
OL,12,F"Across Greater Manchester our
OL,13,Fofficer's day-in and day-out serve to
OL,14,Fprotect the public in the best way
OL,15,Fthey can and that often means putting
OL,16,Fthemselves in harm's way as the first
OL,17,Fline of defence."
